Author: SubBiscuit
Text: I didn't think I was that bad and I'm not UW but I went in for my assessment and they said I practically needed IP.  It's a behavior disorder. You dont have to look a certain way to need a lot of help. People die from EDs at all ranges of weight.  That said recovery is what you put in - if you dont want to recover it wont magically happen.

Author: temporarymoodswings
Text: The very reason why I don't tell people about my ED is that I just feel like such a dramatic ungrateful bitch. I am also originally from a country where it's just expected from you to suck it up and carry on. "Psychiatrists, therapists?? Pffff, only for the privilaged rich people that are unhappy because their wealth and privilages have spoilt them so much that now they are bored with life."  So sorry you feel this way, I feel ya.
